 Babel, nei pressi del lago Pl\u00e9tipi, e una riserva naturale aperta nel 1996)."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1983650", "itemLabel": "Louis Babel", "dhsid": "044372", "namefr": "Louis Babel", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Babel", "namede": "Louis-Fran\u00e7ois Babel", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis-Fran%C3%A7ois_Babel", "nameit": "Louis Babel", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Babel", "nameen": "Louis Babel", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Babel", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "132508192"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1983650", "wikipedia_page_title": "Louis Babel", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "B", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/044372/2002-12-20"}